            "title": "DNA barcoding of African fruit bats (Mammalia, Pteropodidae). The mitochondrial genome does not provide a reliable discrimination between Epomophorus gambianus and Micropteropus pusillus",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Nicolas",
                    "lastName": "Nesi"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Emmanuel",
                    "lastName": "Nakouné"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
