            "title": "Population genetics as a tool to elucidate pathogen reservoirs: Lessons from Pseudogymnoascus destructans, the causative agent of White-Nose disease in bats",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Nicola M.",
                    "lastName": "Fischer"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
